long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use ChatGPT on any website!

Search or chat with ChatGPT on any website using AISPOT.
A simple and quick way to make ChatGPT searches on any website. Make use of AISPOT search on any website using AISPOT extension.

How it works?

Get your own API key from Open AI and Add your API Key to AISPOT. 

Use the Floating AISPOT button available on any website and start searching or chatting with ChatGPT.

Model: GPT-3.5 supported at this time.

If you are a constant user of ChatGPT and are frequently switching between your work and ChatGPT interface then use AISPOT and make ChatGPT chats on any website.
